  {
    "title": "Fantastische Beschreibung von sibirischen Völkern",
    "sub": "Panel 3 — Oben Mittig",
    "text": "<p>\"<span _d-id=\"1064\" class=\"--l --r container-target\"><span _d-id=\"1070\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Die</span> <span _d-id=\"1074\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Menschen</span> <span _d-id=\"1078\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">hier</span> <span _d-id=\"1082\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">sind</span> <span _d-id=\"1086\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">nachtaktiv</span>; <span _d-id=\"1090\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">tagsüber</span> <span _d-id=\"1094\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">halten</span> <span _d-id=\"1098\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">sie</span> <span _d-id=\"1102\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">sich</span> <span _d-id=\"1106\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">versteckt</span>, <span _d-id=\"1110\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">während</span> <span _d-id=\"1114\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">sie</span> <span _d-id=\"1118\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">nachts</span> <span _d-id=\"1122\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">aktiv</span> <span _d-id=\"1126\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">sind</span>. <span _d-id=\"1130\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Sie</span> <span _d-id=\"1134\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">bedecken</span> <span _d-id=\"1138\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">ihren</span> <span _d-id=\"1142\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Körper</span> <span _d-id=\"1146\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">mit</span> <span _d-id=\"1150\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Hirschfellen</span>. <span _d-id=\"1154\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Sie</span> <span _d-id=\"1158\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">haben</span> <span _d-id=\"1162\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">dieselben</span> <span _d-id=\"1166\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Ohren</span>, <span _d-id=\"1170\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Augen</span> <span _d-id=\"1174\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">und</span> <span _d-id=\"1178\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Nasen</span> <span _d-id=\"1182\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">wie</span> <span _d-id=\"1186\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Menschen</span>, <span _d-id=\"1190\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">doch</span> <span _d-id=\"1194\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">ihr</span> <span _d-id=\"1198\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Mund</span> <span _d-id=\"1202\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">befindet</span> <span _d-id=\"1206\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">sich</span> <span _d-id=\"1210\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">oben</span> <span _d-id=\"1214\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">auf</span> <span _d-id=\"1218\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">dem</span> <span _d-id=\"1222\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Kopf</span>. <span _d-id=\"1226\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Sie</span> <span _d-id=\"1230\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">ernähren</span> <span _d-id=\"1234\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">sich</span> <span _d-id=\"1238\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">von</span> <span _d-id=\"1242\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Hirschen</span> <span _d-id=\"1246\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">und</span> <span _d-id=\"1250\" class=\"--l --r hover:bg-surface-info-muted hover:text-info-muted\">Schlangen</span>.</span>\" Viele der Beschreibungen von Völkern in Gebieten, die wenig erkundet und erforscht waren, sind mit oft herabwürdigenden Beschreibungen beschriftet, die reine Fantasie sind und nichts mit der Realität zu tun haben.</p>",
